{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"202d7a11fc","title":"在公安部关于处理在押病残战犯报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"37a480be4d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":2,"day":2,"articleId":"202d7a11fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"37af2d1ae2","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"202d7a11fc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指公安部党组1957年1月29日关于处理在押病残战犯给中央的请示报告中提出的刘焕东等12名蒋介石集团的战犯。考虑到他们在关押期同患有重病，有的因病致残，而表现一般较好，公安部与最高人民检察院、最高人民法院商妥，拟准予保外就医。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b79cd24115","type":"title","text":"在公安部关于处理在押病残战犯报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"202d7a11fc"},{"id":"37af2d1ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"不但这些人”应当处理，其他战犯凡犯罪较轻、表现较好的，都应考康判决释放，因为已关了七八年了。只留下犯罪较重的和最重的两类，待后处理。请公安部将战犯全体审查一下，定出一个处理方案送中央审阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"202d7a11fc"},{"id":"2896db9e50","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"202d7a11fc"},{"id":"0d62f2d1d2","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"202d7a11fc"}],"page":{"id":"7384c04ed5","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"202d7a11fc","start":272,"end":272}}}},"__N_SSG":true}